content: I can do almost every single thing here that I can do on the computer. Love love love the Xyngular back office app!

I am so grateful for this app! Totally will make my life so much easier! Changing autoship on our phones was crazy! This is soooo much easier. I do keep getting pop ups to update and I can't update or there is no update. Also being able to add someone just got a whole lot easier! Thanks so much for this!
Why do I keep getting a popup when I try to open app from desktop saying, "Please update to latest version in Playstore to continue" then I go to Playstore and there is no update available??

Enjoying the app! Makes changing autoship super easy. Would love to see resources on there too! (Menus, etc)     ***update*** After using the app a few times I really do enjoy it! I've enrolled people using it but it is saving their info and it pops up when typing a new person in. How do I remove their personal info?  ***Update**** seems you have fixed saving the personal info problem. It keeps saying it needs an update but nothing available on google play?
Great app and easy, business is faster

I love the app, super helpful, easy, and convenient. However I was excited to see our detailed commission report (daily bonus, efficiency rating etc) and the app does not have that. Will it be updated to where it will be included? That's the main reason I wanted to have to app.
Loving the new app so far.
Love it helps build your business faster
